---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | V8V88V8V88"
  description="Learn more about Vaibhav Pratap Singh (V8V88V8V88), a Computer Science student interested in Rust, Linux, C++, Web Design, and Cybersecurity."
  canonical="https://v8v88v8v88.com/about/"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Person",
      "url": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/about/",
      "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/about/" },
      "name": "Vaibhav Pratap Singh",
      "alternateName": "V8V88V8V88",
      "jobTitle": "Computer Science Student",
      "description": "A third-year Computer Science student who loves open source and coding.",
      "image": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/images/image.webp",
      "sameAs": [
        "https://github.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://t.me/V8V88V8V88",
        "https://www.youtube.com/c/MagicalV8",
        "https://www.instagram.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://twitter.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://www.reddit.com/user/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://www.linkedin.com/in/v8v88v8v88/",
        "https://fosstodon.org/@v8v88v8v88"
      ],
      "knowsAbout": ["Rust Programming", "Linux", "C++", "C", "GUI Development", "GTK", "QT", "Web Design", "Cybersecurity", "Version Control", "Git", "FOSS"]
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <main class="about-page">
    <div class="bento-grid">
      <div class="bento-item bento-hero clickable" id="hero-card" title="Click to read more">
        <span class="hero-greeting">// about me</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Hi, I'm <span class="name">Vaibhav</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle" id="hero-subtitle">Building, breaking, but always learning.</p>
        <div class="hero-expanded" id="hero-expanded">
          <p>Hi, I'm Vaibhav Pratap Singh, also known as V8 on the internet.</p>
          <p>I'm a computer science student with a minor in AI & ML, but most of my learning has happened outside classrooms. Curiosity, self-learning, and building things from scratch have shaped how I approach computers. Over the years, Linux and open source have become a big part of how I work and think.</p>
          <p>I'm deeply interested in Linux, FOSS, and systems-level software. Understanding how things work internally matters more than surface-level results. This naturally pulled me toward low-level programming, where performance, simplicity, and correctness are important. Lately, I've been spending more time with Rust, exploring it as a safer and more modern systems language.</p>
          <p>My approach to software is heavily influenced by <a href="https://principles-wiki.net/principles:keep_it_simple_stupid" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">KISS</a> and the <a href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Unix_philosophy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Unix philosophy</a>. I prefer simple tools, clear ideas, and minimal abstractions. While I do have experience with full-stack development, it's something I treat as a practical skill, useful when needed and often necessary for earning, but not what excites me the most.</p>
          <p>Alongside programming, I've worked with graphic design and video editing, mostly through community work and personal projects. These skills developed naturally while handling different kinds of computer-related tasks and helped me appreciate the balance between design and engineering.</p>
          <p>I've been actively involved in open-source communities and student tech spaces. From leading and organizing FOSS-related initiatives to helping grow communities like GNOME India and running student groups, community building has been an important part of the journey. Teaching, organizing, and sharing knowledge have helped shape both technical and personal growth.</p>
          <p>Outside of tech, interests often drift into philosophy, history, geography, and scientific reading. A lot of this exploration is driven by curiosity and an ADHD-powered mind that enjoys jumping between ideas. I'm not much of a coffee person. Quiet thinking, late-night experiments, and reading usually work better.</p>
          <p>If any of this resonates with you, feel free to reach out through my <a href="/contact/">social handles</a>. Replies might take some time, but they are always genuine.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="click-hint" id="click-hint">click to read more</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-ascii">
<pre>██╗   ██╗ █████╗ 
██║   ██║██╔══██╗
██║   ██║╚█████╔╝
╚██╗ ██╔╝██╔══██╗
 ╚████╔╝ ╚█████╔╝
  ╚═══╝   ╚════╝ </pre>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-philosophy clickable" id="philosophy-card" title="Click to cycle">
        <p class="section-label">Philosophy</p>
        <div class="philosophy-carousel">
          <p class="philosophy-text active">I believe in <span class="accent">KISS</span> and the <span class="accent">Unix way</span>. Do one thing well.</p>
          <p class="philosophy-text">I appreciate the <span class="accent">Buddhist way</span>. Simplicity, mindfulness, and letting go.</p>
          <p class="philosophy-text">No gods, no masters. Just <span class="accent">logic</span>, <span class="accent">reason</span>, and code.</p>
          <p class="philosophy-text">Question everything. <span class="accent">Doubt</span> is the origin of wisdom.</p>
          <p class="philosophy-text">Life is <span class="accent">impermanent</span>. Build things that outlast you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-stats clickable" id="years-coding" title="Click me">
        <p class="section-label">Years Coding</p>
        <span class="stat-number">8+</span>
        <span class="stat-label" id="years-label">& counting</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-stats">
        <p class="section-label">Glass of Thanda Pani</p>
        <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
        <span class="stat-label">daily required</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-skills">
        <p class="section-label">Tech Stack</p>
        <div class="skills-grid" id="skills-grid">
          <span class="skill-tag highlight">Rust</span>
          <span class="skill-tag highlight">C/C++</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Bash</span>
          <span class="skill-tag highlight">Linux</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">GTK</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Docker</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Neovim</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-currently">
        <div class="currently-heading">
          <span class="section-label">Currently</span>
          <span class="currently-key">Working</span>
        </div>
        <div class="currently-list">
          <div class="currently-item currently-item-work">
            <span class="currently-value"><a href="https://github.com/v8v88v8v88?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="currently-link">Open source projects</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="currently-item">
            <span class="currently-key">Learning</span>
            <span class="currently-value">Rust, ASM & Systems Programming</span>
          </div>
          <div class="currently-item">
            <span class="currently-key">Using</span>
            <span class="currently-value">Fedora + GNOME + Neovim</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-location">
        <span class="location-icon">📍</span>
        <span class="location-text">India</span>
        <span class="location-sub">UTC +5:30</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-cta">
        <p class="cta-text">Let's build something cool?</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact/" class="cta-btn primary">Get in Touch</a>
          <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iQFjSzPWcSA3sAt4WS-uKIUd7ReCz_hz/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn secondary">Resume</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item bento-matrix">
        <canvas id="matrix-canvas"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    var philosophyTexts = document.querySelectorAll('.philosophy-text');
    var philosophyCard = document.getElementById('philosophy-card');
    var currentPhilosophy = 0;
    var autoScrollInterval;
    function rotatePhilosophy() {
      philosophyTexts[currentPhilosophy].classList.remove('active');
      currentPhilosophy = (currentPhilosophy + 1) % philosophyTexts.length;
      philosophyTexts[currentPhilosophy].classList.add('active');
    }
    autoScrollInterval = setInterval(rotatePhilosophy, 4000);
    if (philosophyCard) {
      philosophyCard.addEventListener('click', function() {
        clearInterval(autoScrollInterval);
        rotatePhilosophy();
        autoScrollInterval = setInterval(rotatePhilosophy, 4000);
      });
    }

    var heroCard = document.getElementById('hero-card');
    if (heroCard) {
      heroCard.addEventListener('click', function() { heroCard.classList.toggle('expanded'); });
    }

    var canvas = document.getElementById('matrix-canvas');
    if (canvas) {
      var ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
      function resizeMatrix() { canvas.width = canvas.offsetWidth; canvas.height = canvas.offsetHeight; }
      resizeMatrix();
      window.addEventListener('resize', resizeMatrix);
      var chars = 'アイウエオカキクケコサシスセソタチツテトナニヌネノハヒフヘホマミムメモヤユヨラリルレロワヲン0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ';
      var fontSize = 14;
      var columns = canvas.width / fontSize;
      var drops = [];
      for (var i = 0; i < columns; i++) drops[i] = Math.random() * -100;
      function isLightMode() { return document.body.classList.contains('light-mode'); }
      function drawMatrix() {
        var lightMode = isLightMode();
        ctx.fillStyle = lightMode ? 'rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.1)' : 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)';
        ctx.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
        ctx.fillStyle = lightMode ? '#0f4d1f' : '#1DB954';
        ctx.font = fontSize + 'px JetBrains Mono, monospace';
        for (var i = 0; i < drops.length; i++) {
          var char = chars[Math.floor(Math.random() * chars.length)];
          ctx.fillText(char, i * fontSize, drops[i] * fontSize);
          if (drops[i] * fontSize > canvas.height && Math.random() > 0.975) drops[i] = 0;
          drops[i]++;
        }
      }
      setInterval(drawMatrix, 50);
      window.addEventListener('resize', function() {
        columns = canvas.width / fontSize;
        drops = [];
        for (var i = 0; i < columns; i++) drops[i] = Math.random() * -100;
      });
      var modeSwitch = document.getElementById('mode-switch');
      if (modeSwitch) {
        modeSwitch.addEventListener('change', function() { ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height); });
      }
    }

    var skillTags = document.querySelectorAll('.skill-tag');
    skillTags.forEach(function(tag) {
      tag.style.cursor = 'pointer';
      tag.addEventListener('click', function() { tag.classList.toggle('highlight'); });
    });

    var yearsCoding = document.getElementById('years-coding');
    var yearsLabel = document.getElementById('years-label');
    if (yearsCoding && yearsLabel) {
      var originalLabel = yearsLabel.textContent;
      yearsCoding.addEventListener('click', function() {
        if (yearsLabel.textContent === originalLabel) {
          yearsLabel.textContent = "wasn't consistent at all so it's a bogus shit XD";
          yearsLabel.style.fontSize = '0.6rem';
          yearsLabel.style.color = '#1DB954';
        } else {
          yearsLabel.textContent = originalLabel;
          yearsLabel.style.fontSize = '';
          yearsLabel.style.color = '';
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* PASTE THE FULL ABOUT PAGE CSS FROM THE ORIGINAL about/index.html <style> block here */
.about-page {
  min-height: 100vh;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 104px clamp(1rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem) 3rem;
}
.bento-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
.bento-item { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 18px; padding: 1.25rem 1.2rem; transition: all 0.3s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); }
.bento-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 70%; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25), transparent); }
.bento-item:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); transform: translateY(-4px); }
.section-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35); letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
.bento-hero { grid-column: span 8; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: 220px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero-greeting { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #1DB954; margin-bottom: 0.55rem; }
.hero-title { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 400; color: #fff; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
.hero-title .name { font-style: italic; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); transition: color 0.3s ease; }
.bento-hero:hover .hero-title .name { color: #1DB954 !important; }
.hero-subtitle { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); max-width: 400px; }
.bento-item.bento-ascii { min-width: 0; }
.bento-ascii { grid-column: span 4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 220px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: clamp(0.45rem, 0.65vw + 0.35rem, 0.6rem); line-height: 1.15; color: #1DB954; white-space: pre; text-align: center; }
.bento-ascii pre { margin: 0; width: fit-content; max-width: 100%; min-width: 0; margin-inline: auto; box-sizing: border-box; }
.bento-philosophy { grid-column: span 6; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 1.35rem; gap: 0.75rem; }
.bento-philosophy > .section-label { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
.philosophy-carousel { position: relative; min-height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.philosophy-text { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-style: italic; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); line-height: 1.5; position: absolute; opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; pointer-events: none; }
.philosophy-text.active { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); pointer-events: auto; }
.philosophy-text .accent { color: #1DB954; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }
.bento-item.clickable { cursor: pointer; }
.bento-item.clickable:hover { border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); }
.hero-expanded { display: none; margin-top: 1.1rem; padding-top: 1.1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
.hero-expanded p { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }
.hero-expanded p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.bento-hero.expanded .hero-expanded { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
.click-hint { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); position: absolute; bottom: 1rem; right: 1.5rem; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
.bento-hero.expanded .click-hint { display: none; }
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
.bento-stats { grid-column: span 3; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
.stat-number { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 2.65rem; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; line-height: 1; }
.stat-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 0.35rem; }
.bento-skills { grid-column: span 6; }
.skills-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.48rem; }
.skill-tag { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); padding: 0.38rem 0.85rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); border-radius: 100px; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
.skill-tag:hover { color: #1DB954; border-color: rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.3); background: rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.1); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.skill-tag.highlight { color: #1DB954; border-color: rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.3); background: rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.1); }
.bento-currently { grid-column: span 6; }
.currently-heading { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.65rem; }
.currently-heading .section-label { margin-bottom: 0; }
.currently-item-work .currently-value { display: block; }
.currently-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.65rem; }
.currently-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline; }
.currently-key { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; min-width: 80px; }
.currently-value { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); }
.currently-link { color: #1DB954; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.3); transition: all 0.2s ease; }
.currently-link:hover { color: #22d35e; border-bottom-color: #22d35e; }
.bento-location { grid-column: span 3; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
.location-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.45rem; }
.location-text { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); }
.location-sub { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
.bento-matrix { grid-column: span 3; padding: 0; overflow: hidden; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%), #000; }
.bento-matrix canvas { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
.bento-cta { grid-column: span 6; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
.cta-text { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 0.65rem; }
.cta-btn { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.62rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 100px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
.cta-btn.primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f4d1f 0%, #1DB954 100%); color: #fff; }
.cta-btn.primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(29, 185, 84, 0.3); }
.cta-btn.secondary { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); color: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
.cta-btn.secondary:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }

:global(body.light-mode) .bento-item { background: #f8f8f8; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); }
:global(body.light-mode) .bento-item::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06), transparent); }
:global(body.light-mode) .bento-item:hover { background: #fff; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12); box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); }
:global(body.light-mode) .section-label { color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35); }
:global(body.light-mode) .bento-hero { background: #f8f8f8; }
:global(body.light-mode) .hero-greeting { color: #0f4d1f; }
:global(body.light-mode) .hero-title { color: #1d1d1f; }
:global(body.light-mode) .hero-title .name { color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); transition: color 0.3s ease; }
